title: Surprise Chocolate Box Necklace by CrazyWorldOfVal X FT
description:
These CrazyWorldOfVal X Fluffy Tori necklaces are handmade by Val herself. They are made to match the Mots Doux à ma Chérie collection, so they're the perfect piece of jewelry to go with our dresses.

Val is a jewelry designer and took inspiration from the print. She decided to replicate the chocolate box, which she found so cute that she wanted to turn it into a fun piece of jewelry, a kind of wearable miniature.

The necklaces come in two colorways (red or pink), so you can get the color that best matches the dress you choose!

They are very limited necklaces and they are all made of acrylic, resin and hand sculpted fimo clay pieces.

This collab piece is brought to you by Fluffy Tori in Switzerland. It ships from our US warehouse.

title: Lovely Oracle Necklace
description:
Call on the wisdom and magical power of your Friends on the Other Side with the new Lovely Oracle Necklace by starcrossed lovelies! This planchette inspired necklace is sure to aid you in your journey to commune with the spirit world, as it features the phases of the Moon, magical wings, stars, glittering black stones and a dangling crystal! After all, there's no reason you can't carry out your rituals and be kawaii at the same time! Choose from our dusty pink or purple versions of this necklace - both are full of witchy power!

This necklace chain consists of hand beaded clear and black glass beads and silver moons, along with a silver chain. The necklace is roughly 18 inches in length, but can be adjusted to 20 inches. Please note, although reactions are rare, this chain is not considered hypoallergenic. Please be aware if you are sensitive to metals!

title: Froggy Friend Ring
description:
Well hello there, friendo! Looking for a companion to join you on your journey through the woods? Let this Froggy Friend join you as you visit the local baker, shop for fresh veggies, or even just relax in the fresh spring air during a picnic! No matter the occasion, your new Froggy Friend will be there, smiling up at you and cheering you on!

This adorable little frog by starcrossed lovelies is attached to an adjustable ring back to fit a variety of sizes.

Due to the handmade quality of these pieces, slight variations in color and imperfections may occur.

description:

❥Handmade resin pendant
❥Satin ribbon
❥Silver tone stainless steel beaded chain
❥Chain length: 24"
❥Pendant size: approximately 1.5"
❥Lobster clasp closure
❥Extender chain for adjustability of length ~2"

☆Due to the handmade nature of the item, each individual piece will vary slightly.
☆Color may differ slightly depending on your screen settings.

☆Resin Jewelry Care☆
To keep the colors of your resin jewelry vibrant, it is recommended to store the jewelry in a cool, dark place away from sunlight, such as a jewelry box or drawer.
This item is made by Sweet Juju in the USA. It ships from our US warehouse.

title: Dried Blue Flower Terrarium Globe Necklace
description:
Long loved event-only terrarium jewelry are now available here on Etsy!

A little bit of paradise has been captured beneath the dome of this terrarium necklace. Dried flowers lightly dyed blue sit under the glass dome.

Necklace is approximately 20" long.
The pendants are very hardy and do not easily break!
The necklace comes with a middle connector and two bows in the chain, with lobster clasp.

We can make the necklace longer or shorter if needed. We can also remove the bows so the necklace is just a terrarium pendant on a chain. These alterations are free- just let us know in the comments section or via message after your purchase.

We do take custom orders to create your own miniature paradise, pending availability of supplies. Just send us a message!

Please be sure to read the policies of the shop before purchasing!

Made by Paradise Rose Shop. Item ships directly from vendor.

title: Glittery Vampire Pumpkin Earrings
description:
This piece is from the Gramarye 2020 Halloween release.

This series is one of a kind and will not be produced again. The earrings feature an orange pumpkin. Yes, it's a vampire pumpkin with bats as eyebrows. This pair of earrings has some transparency, so you can put them up to the light and they will sparkle!

There is a matching necklace to this earring set! This listing is for the earrings only.

Earrings are approximately .75" in diameter.

Each item is a one of a kind item and all handmade by myself, so minor imperfections may occur. Nevertheless, I strive to create a beautiful item that you will enjoy. Please note that differences in monitor display color settings may mean there is a slight color variance. Rest assured, the photos taken here have been taken in natural light with little to no editing. No filter or color variation was applied.

Care instructions- Be sure to store in a dark place and not in direct sunlight. It can be worn in sunlight with no worry, but long exposure to direct sun is not recommended. Chain and pendant can be cleaned with a dry, clean cloth. 

  • This item is shipping from Paradise Rose Shop in California, USA!
